{"tid":694074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勁過唐琳玲，外國有教徒搵耶穌上庭做辯護律師","createTime":"2018-06-08T04:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T04:23:08.000Z","uid":130105,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b63dbe5def6943a724ae23dc2150d02bb012f11f","tid":694074,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T04:14:09.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 ，話個公仔係耶穌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Religious couple loses custody of their baby daughter after a stuffed lion the parents claimed was Jesus Christ acted as their lawyer</span><br />\n <ul><br />\n&bull;A hyper-religious couple in Canada have lost custody of their daughter <br />\n&bull;The couple went to court to fight the decision, but it backfired terribly <br />\n&bull;During trial they used a stuffed lion as their lawyer and claimed it was Jesus<br />\n&bull;They spoke to lion in tongues, told witnesses Jesus was speaking through them<br />\n</ul> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/06/07/15/4D04AAED00000578-5817213-image-a-17_1528382935284.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F15%2F4D04AAED00000578-5817213-image-a-17_1528382935284.jpg&h=39c688dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n A Canadian couple have lost custody of their child after having a stuffed lion they claimed was Jesus represent them in court and communicating with it via tongues (stock image)<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5817213/Religious-couple-loses-child-custody-stuffed-lion-parents-say-Jesus-acted-lawyer.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-5817213%2FReligious-couple-loses-child-custody-stuffed-lion-parents-say-Jesus-acted-lawyer.html&d=QuZdVptXGdPlftUvT%2Bye5gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%